### Profil laden
GET http://localhost:8080/api/profile/{{userId}}

### Spiel starten (Beispiel TicTacToe mit Gandalf)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/game/session
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userId": "{{userId}}",
  "gameType": "TICTACTOE",
  "playerTheme": "GANDALF"
}

### Spiel beenden (Beispiel-Session)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/game/session/{{sessionId}}/finish
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "score": 42,
  "metadata": { "result": "WIN" }
}

### Leaderboard abfragen
GET http://localhost:8080/api/game/leaderboard?gameType=TICTACTOE&playerTheme=GANDALF
